<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/civil-justice-council> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Civil Justice Council (CJC) is responsible for overseeing and co-ordinating the modernisation of the civil justice system. CJC is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Justice ."@en .
